---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Data Analyst Case Studies for Startups | Isabella Rondon"
  description="Real projects. Real results. See how Isabella Rondon built financial data pipelines on GCP, automated QuickBooks reporting with Python, and developed custom AI agents for US-based businesses."
>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://isabellarondon.com/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Case Studies", "item": "https://isabellarondon.com/case-studies/" }
    ]
  })} />

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Case Studies</div>
      <h1>What Changes When<br><span class="accent-light">Data Works</span></h1>
      <p>Three engagements across ETL automation, financial data strategy, and AI agent development.</p>
      <p class="page-header-tagline">Real clients, real numbers, real impact.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- CASE STUDIES GRID -->
  <section class="cs-index-section">
    <div class="cs-index-grid">

      <a href="/case-studies/financial-reporting-automation" class="cs-index-card">
        <div class="cs-index-tag">ETL Pipeline &amp; Automation</div>
        <h2 class="cs-index-headline">2 days of manual QuickBooks work every week. Now a Python pipeline runs it daily — for 8 companies at once.</h2>
        <p class="cs-index-sub">The VP of Finance at a US-based education holding company was spending 2 full days a week on manual data exports. I built a Python automation pipeline on GCP that eliminated that entirely.</p>
        <div class="cs-index-stats">
          <div class="cs-index-stat">
            <div class="cs-index-stat-value">16 hrs<span>/week</span></div>
            <div class="cs-index-stat-label">recovered for the finance team</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-index-stat">
            <div class="cs-index-stat-value">100%</div>
            <div class="cs-index-stat-label">data accuracy</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-index-stat">
            <div class="cs-index-stat-value">8</div>
            <div class="cs-index-stat-label">entities automated simultaneously</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-index-link">Read case study →</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/case-studies/financial-data-strategy" class="cs-index-card">
        <div class="cs-index-tag">Data Strategy · Workflow Automation</div>
        <h2 class="cs-index-headline">Days of cross-departmental reconciliation, full of manual errors, across 400+ corporate clients. I built the infrastructure that replaced it.</h2>
        <p class="cs-index-sub">A B2B financial services company with 400+ corporate clients was running critical operations on manual exports, siloed spreadsheets, and informal messaging channels. I rebuilt how they managed their data from the ground up.</p>
        <div class="cs-index-stats">
          <div class="cs-index-stat">
            <div class="cs-index-stat-value">99%</div>
            <div class="cs-index-stat-label">fewer reconciliation errors</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-index-stat">
            <div class="cs-index-stat-value">&lt;1hr</div>
            <div class="cs-index-stat-label">reconciliation time (was days)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-index-stat">
            <div class="cs-index-stat-value">400+</div>
            <div class="cs-index-stat-label">corporate clients covered</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-index-link">Read case study →</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/case-studies/ai-sales-agent-car-dealership" class="cs-index-card">
        <div class="cs-index-tag">AI Agent Development</div>
        <h2 class="cs-index-headline">Most people talk about what an AI agent could do. Here's how this one talks to customers.</h2>
        <p class="cs-index-sub">Built a fully functional AI sales agent for a car dealership — trained on their real business rules, integrated with their actual systems, and ready to deploy.</p>
        <div class="cs-index-stats">
          <div class="cs-index-stat">
            <div class="cs-index-stat-value">24/7</div>
            <div class="cs-index-stat-label">availability — no staff needed</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-index-stat">
            <div class="cs-index-stat-value">5</div>
            <div class="cs-index-stat-label">automated workflows</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-index-stat">
            <div class="cs-index-stat-value">100%</div>
            <div class="cs-index-stat-label">custom-built, zero templates</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-index-link">Read case study →</div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA FINAL -->
  <div class="cta-final">
    <div class="cta-final-left">
      <div class="cta-final-label">Ready to build?</div>
      <h2 class="cta-final-headline">Your startup needs a data foundation.<br>Let's build it right.</h2>
      <p class="cta-final-sub">Book a 30-minute discovery call. We'll figure out exactly what you need — and whether I'm the right person to build it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-final-right">
      <a href="https://cal.com/isabella-rondon-jrkvbh/30min" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a Discovery Call &nbsp;→</a>
      <span class="cta-note">No commitment. 30 minutes.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
